Justin Long and Emmy Rossum are star-crossed lovers whose relationship

 dazzlingly original romance. When a chance encounter brings together
 the cynical Dell (Long) and the quick-witted Kimberly (Rossum), the

unforgettable portrait of a relationship emerges. Sumptuously shot

one-of-a-kind cosmic love story.
